chunk_content: definition: Provision of key staff or commodities for VMMC includes: medical instruments, supplies, or medicines needed for the VMMC procedure, or funding for salaries for HCW who deliver VMMC services. Ongoing support for VMMC service delivery improvement includes: training of VMMC service providers; clinical mentoring and supportive supervision of HCW at VMMC sites; infrastructure/facility renovation; support of VMMC service-related data collection, reporting, data quality assessments (DQA); CQI/EQA of VMMC services at point of service delivery; or commodities consumption forecasting and supply chain management support. Guiding narrative 1. Briefly describe any safety improvement activities that were implemented during the reporting questions: quarter (e.g., responses to adverse events, provider trainings, updated safety guidelines, etc.) 2.
